Where can you find the environments within a deployment?
UI->Manage->environments

Where do you find the toolkit path for an environment?
UI->Manage->environments scroll down in center pane to "toolkit path"

Toolkit Path
/var/tmp


How can I determine access credentials for an environment user?
UI->Manage->Environments->click on user in center pane under "ENVIRONMENT USERS",
then, click the pencil icon and you will be redirected to the authentication type
page, it's called "Login Type".

kgrh79ora1911src.dcol2.delphix.com -> username and password(oracle/oracle)
kgrh79ora1911tgt.dcol2.delphix.com -> username and public key
